      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALL I SEE (4) jumped from the pinch last start to lead all the way and score (29.61) at this track in Mix 6/7 over 515m. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Expected to be right there at the finish again. OTTO ROSE (2) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors four starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (30.18) at The Meadows over 525m. Expected to feature again. PAW BRUTUS (8) has been out of the placings last couple but caught the eye when clocking a 30.04 over 525m at The Meadows three starts back. Must include on winning run three back. INCLINATION (6) was impressive in a dynamic 29.79 win last start. Each way chance.",
